{"kanda":6,"sarga":79,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"निर्गतंमकराक्षंतेदृष्टवावानरपुङ्गवाः ।आप्लुत्यसहसासर्वेयोद्धुकामाव्यवस्थिताः","trans":"On seeing Maka raksha all the Vanara chiefs returned, jumped, and stood ready enthusiastically to fight.","words":[{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"ते","m":"those"},{"d":"निर्गतम्","m":"returning"},{"d":"मकराक्षम्","m":"Maka raksha"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"आप्लुत्य","m":"jumped"},{"d":"योद्धुकामाः","m":"enthusiastic to fight"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"ततःप्रवृत्तंसुमहत्तद्युद्धंरोमहर्षणम् ।निशाचरैःप्लवङ्गानांदेवानांदानवैरिव","trans":"Then ensued a battle between Rakshasas and Vanaras whichcaused horripilation, just like the battle between Devas and Danavas.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"प्लवङ्गानाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"निशाचरैः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"देवेनाम्","m":"Devas"},{"d":"तत्","m":"there"},{"d":"सुहत्","m":"together"},{"d":"रोहर्षणम्","m":"one's hair stand to raise"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"battle"},{"d":"प्रवृत्तम्","m":"ensued"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"वृक्षशूलनिपातैश्चशिलापरिघपातनैः ।अन्योन्यंमर्दयन्तिस्मतदाकपिनिशाचराः","trans":"Then monkeys as well as Rakshasas fought hurling trees and pikes and bringing down rocks and clubs physically hurting each other.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"कपिनिशाचराः","m":"monkeys and Rakshasas"},{"d":"वृक्षशूलनिपातैः च","m":"trees and pikes"},{"d":"अन्योन्यम्","m":"one another"},{"d":"मर्दयन्तिस्म","m":"physically hurting each other."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"शक्तिखडगगदाकुन्तैस्तोमरैश्चनिशाचराः ।पट्टसैर्भिण्ढिपालैश्चबाणपातैःसमन्ततः पाशमुद्गरदण्डैश्चनिखातैश्चापरेस्तथा ।कदनंकपिसिंहानांचक्रुस्तेरजनीचराः","trans":"Those prowlers, then ight rangers discharging javelins, swords, maces, spears, lances, small swords, bhindi Palas, shafts, nooses, mallets and staff and other weapons on the lions among the monkeys, caused destruction.","words":[{"d":"तोमरैश्च","m":"lances"},{"d":"पट्टसै:","m":"small swords"},{"d":"पाशमुद्गरदण्डैः च","m":"nooses, mallets, and staffs"},{"d":"तथा","m":"like that"},{"d":"अन्यैश्च","m":"and other weapons"},{"d":"समन्ततः","m":"discharging"},{"d":"कपिसिंहानाम्","m":"lions among monkeys"},{"d":"कदनम्","m":"destruction"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"शक्तिखडगगदाकुन्तैस्तोमरैश्चनिशाचराः ।पट्टसैर्भिण्ढिपालैश्चबाणपातैःसमन्ततः पाशमुद्गरदण्डैश्चनिखातैश्चापरेस्तथा ।कदनंकपिसिंहानांचक्रुस्तेरजनीचराः","trans":"Those prowlers, then ight rangers discharging javelins, swords, maces, spears, lances, small swords, bhindi Palas, shafts, nooses, mallets and staff and other weapons on the lions among the monkeys, caused destruction.","words":[{"d":"तोमरैश्च","m":"lances"},{"d":"पट्टसै:","m":"small swords"},{"d":"पाशमुद्गरदण्डैः च","m":"nooses, mallets, and staffs"},{"d":"तथा","m":"like that"},{"d":"अन्यैश्च","m":"and other weapons"},{"d":"समन्ततः","m":"discharging"},{"d":"कपिसिंहानाम्","m":"lions among monkeys"},{"d":"कदनम्","m":"destruction"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"बाणौघैरर्दिताश्चापिखरपुत्रेणवानराः ।सम्भ्रान्तमनसस्सर्वेदुद्रुवुर्भयपीडिताः","trans":"Vanaras perturbed terribly by the volley of arrows of Khara's son were stricken with fear and ran.","words":[{"d":"खरपुत्रेण","m":"by Khara's son"},{"d":"बाणौघैः","m":"by volley of arrows"},{"d":"अर्धिताः","m":"stricken"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"वानराः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"सम्भ्रान्तमनसः","m":"perturbed terribly"},{"d":"भयपीडिताः","m":"stricken with fear"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"तान्दृष्टवाराक्षसास्सर्वेद्रवमाणान्वलीमुखान् ।नेदुस्तेसिम्हवद्दृष्टाराक्षसाजितकाशिनः","trans":"The monkeys saw all the arrogant Rakshasas roaring like lions and running as though triumphed.","words":[{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"तान्","m":"their"},{"d":"द्रवमाणान्","m":"running"},{"d":"वलीमुखान्","m":"monkeys"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"नेदुः","m":"arrogant"},{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"सिम्हवत्","m":"like lion roar"},{"d":"दृष्टा","m":"seeing"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"विद्रवत्सुतदातेषुवानरेषुसमन्ततः ।रामस्तान्वारमायासशरवर्षेणराक्षसान्","trans":"Thereafter, seeing the Vanaras running all over, Rama stopped the Rakshasas by rain of arrows.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"तेषु","m":"them"},{"d":"वानरेषु","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"विद्रवत्सु","m":"running"},{"d":"शरवर्षेण","m":"by rain of arrows"},{"d":"तान्","m":"them"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"वारयामास","m":"stopped."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"रितान्राक्षसान्दृष्टवामकराक्षोनिशाचरः ।क्रोधानलसमाविष्टोवचनंचेदमब्रवीत्","trans":"Seeing the intercepted Rakshasas, the night ranger Maka raksha was overtaken by fire of anger spoke these words.","words":[{"d":"वारितान्","m":"intercepted"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"this"},{"d":"वचनं च","m":"words"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"तिष्ठराम मयासार्धंद्वन्द्वयुद्धंददामिते ।त्याजयिष्यामितेप्राणान् धनुर्मुक्सैशशितैश्शरैः","trans":"\"Rama Stop. Duel will take place with me. I will give you sharpened arrows from my bow and relieve you of your life.\"","words":[{"d":"राम","m":"Rama"},{"d":"तिष्ठ","m":"stop"},{"d":"मयासार्धम्","m":"with me will take place"},{"d":"शितैः","m":"sharpened"},{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"द्वन्ध्वयुद्धम्","m":"duel fight"},{"d":"भविष्यति","m":"will give you"},{"d":"धनुर्मुक्स्सैः","m":"arrows release from my bow"},{"d":"ददामि","m":"will give you"},{"d":"प्राणान्","m":"life"},{"d":"त्याजयिष्यामि","m":"relieve you"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"यत्तदादण्डकारण्येपितरंहतवान्मम ।तदग्रतःस्वकर्मस्थंदृष्टवारोषोऽभिवर्धते","trans":"\"Then in Dandakaranya my father was killed. Now for the samereason you are in front of me. Seeing you my anger is increasing.\"","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"दण्डकारण्ये","m":"in D and akaranya"},{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"पितरम्","m":"father"},{"d":"यत्","m":"there"},{"d":"हतवान्","m":"was killed"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"स्वकर्मस्थम्","m":"for the same cause"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"अभिवर्धते","m":"is increasing"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"दह्यन्तेधृशमङ्गानिदुरात्मन्ममराघव ।यन्मयासि न दृष्टस्त्वंतस्मिन् कालेमहावने","trans":"\"O Evil minded Raghava! at that time, I did not see you in D and aka forest. My limbs are burning in anger.\"","words":[{"d":"दुरात्मन्","m":"evil minded"},{"d":"राघव","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"तस्मिन् काले","m":"at that mean time"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"your"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"महावने","m":"in the great forest (D and aka)"},{"d":"यत्","m":"there"},{"d":"न दृष्टः","m":"no seen असि by"},{"d":"मम","m":"me"},{"d":"अङ्गानि","m":"limbs"},{"d":"भृशम्","m":"in anger"},{"d":"दह्यन्ते","m":"burning"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"दिष्ट्यासिदर्शनंराम ममत्वंप्राप्तवानिह ।काङ्क्षितोऽसिक्षुधार्तस्यसिंहस्येवेतरोमृगः","trans":"\"Rama! To my good fortune it became possible for me to see you here. Just as a hungry lion waits for an animal, I am waiting for you.\"","words":[{"d":"राम","m":"Rama"},{"d":"दिष्ट्या","m":"good fortune"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"इह","m":"here"},{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"दर्शनम्","m":"seen"},{"d":"प्राप्तवान्","m":"became possible"},{"d":"क्षधार्तस्य","m":"hungry"},{"d":"सिंहस्य","m":"lion's"},{"d":"इह","m":"here"},{"d":"मृगःइव","m":"like animal"},{"d":"असि","m":"I am"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"अद्यमद्बाणवेगेनप्रेतराडिवषयंगतः ।येत्वयानिहताःशूराःसहतैश्चसमेष्यसि","trans":"\"Now by the speed of my arrow I will send you totherealm of Yama and there you will be along with the demons killed by you.\"","words":[{"d":"अद्य","m":"now"},{"d":"मद्भाणवेगेन","m":"by the speed of my arrow"},{"d":"प्रेतराडिवषयम्","m":"the realm of Yama"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"you"},{"d":"ये","m":"there"},{"d":"निहताः","m":"killed"},{"d":"तैःसह","m":"with them"},{"d":"समेष्यसि च","m":"will send you"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"बहुनात्रकिमुक्तेनशृणुराम वचोमम ।पश्यन्तुसकलालोकास्त्वा, मांचैवरणाजिरे","trans":"\"Rama, why talk so much? Listen to my words. Let people in all worldssee you and me in the battlefield.\"","words":[{"d":"राम","m":"Rama"},{"d":"अत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"बहुना","m":"many"},{"d":"उक्तेन","m":"talk"},{"d":"किम्","m":"why"},{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"वचः","m":"words"},{"d":"शृणु","m":"listen"},{"d":"सकलाः","m":"all"},{"d":"रणाजिरे","m":"in the field of battle"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"your"},{"d":"मांचैव","m":"me too"},{"d":"पश्यन्तु","m":"will see"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"अस्त्रैर्वागदयावापिबाहुभ्यांवामहाहवे ।अभ्यस्तंयेनवाराम तेनैवयुधिवर्तताम्","trans":"\"By weapons, or by mace or else with hand s or any other weapon or with your military practice, you fight, he said to Rama.\"","words":[{"d":"राम","m":"Rama"},{"d":"अस्त्रैर्वा","m":"by weapons"},{"d":"गदयावापि","m":"or by mace"},{"d":"येन","m":"or else"},{"d":"अभ्यस्तम्","m":"with hands"},{"d":"तेनैव","m":"any one"},{"d":"महाहवे","m":"military practice"},{"d":"युधि","m":"fight"},{"d":"वर्तताम्","m":"said"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"मकराक्ष्वचश्श्रुत्वारामोदशरथात्मजः ।अब्रवीत्प्रहसन्वाक्यमुत्तरोत्तरवादिनम्","trans":"Laughing at the words of Maka raksha who was speaking again and again Rama said.","words":[{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"on hearing"},{"d":"प्रहसन्","m":"laughing"},{"d":"उत्तरोत्तरवादिनम्","m":"speaking again and again"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"said"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"कत्थसेकिंवृथारक्षो बहून्यसदृशानिते ।न रणेशक्यतेजेतुंविनायुद्धेनवाग्भलात्","trans":"\"Rakshasa! Why so much of wasteful talk about What you can't accomplish? Victory is not possible on the battlefield with your force of speech\"","words":[{"d":"रक्षः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"असदृशानि","m":"in What can't be accomplished"},{"d":"बहूनि","m":"many"},{"d":"वृथा","m":"wasteful"},{"d":"किंकत्थसे","m":"why indulge"},{"d":"युद्धेनविना","m":"without war"},{"d":"वाग्भलात्","m":"force of speech"},{"d":"रणे","m":"in war"},{"d":"जेतुम्","m":"victory"},{"d":"ते","m":"by you"},{"d":"न शक्यम्","m":"not possible"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"चतुर्दशसहस्राणिरक्षसांत्वत्पिता च यः ।त्रिशिरादूषणश्चापिदण्डकेनिहतामया","trans":"\"In Dandaka, fourteen thousand Rakshasas, your father, Trisira, and also Dooshana were killed by me alone.\"","words":[{"d":"दण्डके","m":"in Dandaka"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me alone"},{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"चतुर्दश","m":"fourteen"},{"d":"सहस्राणि","m":"thousands"},{"d":"यः","m":"there"},{"d":"त्व